==English==
===Verb===
'''[[look]] [[forward]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[anticipate]] or [[expect]]; especially, to expect something to be [[pleasant]].
#:''I enjoyed his writing very much, and I '''look forward''' to meeting him in person.''

